# 3. Workflow Business Dashboard

This is often the dashboard product owners like.

Show:

* Total workflows today
* Running workflows
* Completed workflows
* Failed workflows
* Average workflow duration
* Workflows per tenant/user
* Top failing workflow types
* Workflow success rate

Example cards:

```
Running Workflows      124
Completed Today      13,542
Failed Today            52
Avg Duration         18 sec
Success Rate        99.6%
```

